    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major wear. Mechanically, the car is solid, shifts smoothly, and has a complete service history. It offers a reliable and pleasant driving experience for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
