    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid foundation for a buyer willing to address some minor mechanical and cosmetic needs. The exterior features several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows typical wear for its age. Mechanically, it starts and runs, though it would benefit from a tune-up and new tires soon. It represents a functional option for someone looking for an affordable daily driver with a bit of character.",
      "price": 18000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
